  "description": "A series of animated shorts centered on the fictional polar bear and main character of the same name. <br><br>\r\nEach three-minute episode focuses on the bear's curiosity and have many moments of slapstick. Bernard never speaks with the exception of unintelligible noises.<br><br>\r\nBernard is accompanied in the cartoons by a few other characters: Lloyd and Eva the penguins, Zack the lizard, Goliat(h) the chihuahua, Sam the baby, Pilot the dog, Pokey the porcupine and Santa Claus.<br><br>\r\nHe usually gets knocked unconscious or severely injured at the end of an episode, due to some calamity caused by his bumbling.<br><br>\r\n(Source: Wikipedia)",
